{"tid":2070120,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"桂格燕麥旗下品牌包裝涉種族歧視將撤換","createTime":"2020-06-19T02:13:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-19T06:26:25.000Z","uid":104804,"like":1,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"59102fbeccb0f71b51d07a0ac9219164978d20ca","tid":2070120,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=394902\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394902&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=e1c71fc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D394902&h=95613bfe\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=394902</a><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】美國黑人弗洛伊德死亡案，令反種族歧視成為一股潮流。桂格燕麥旗下一個有逾130年歷史的品牌，包裝亦因為被指涉及種族歧視而被撤換，品牌亦要重新命名。<br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》報道，百事公司擁有的貴格燕麥，旗下有131年歷史的品牌「傑邁瑪阿姨」，產品以黑人女性畫像作為包裝，被指涉及種族歧視，公司在壓力下宣布換掉包裝設計並更改品牌名稱。<br />\n<br />\n1889年創立的「傑邁瑪阿姨」，主要售賣美式鬆餅粉、糖漿及其他早餐食品，是貴格燕麥旗下其中一個主要品牌。<br />\n<br />\n產品包裝上的黑人女子畫像，在1893年已開始使用，畫中人是品牌創辦人，根據一名黑奴形象繪畫，之後雖然曾多次更新，但仍一直被人質疑有種族歧視之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n黑人女歌手柯比早前上載短片，談及品牌歷史，又教人製作沒有種族歧視早餐，將鬆餅粉倒入廚房鋅盆內。短片短短數日就獲得超過180萬點擊率，令「傑邁瑪阿姨」的種族歧視問題再次成為焦點。<br />\n<br />\n百事公司發聲明指，意識到品牌的包裝和形象起源於種族偏見，決定將產品系統重新命名及設計新的包裝，希望可以推動種族平等。<br />\n<br />\n新包裝將於今年第四季推出，至於新名稱就要稍後再公布。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cZnsDyT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcZnsDyT.jpg&h=2a49ebf1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c30c29a193347e46bd53edf88071ea71cac4c6df","tid":2070120,"uid":104804,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:14:48.000Z","msg":"右邊個女主播好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6744be1715e47fe76562f1fcf0fe07e39b2c51b6","tid":2070120,"uid":237487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:16:09.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: right;\">同我入嚟like 女拔 楊老師個page + 課金預訂佢本書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2070055\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2070055</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</div><br />\n<br />\nFb<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lc.ryeung/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flc.ryeung%2F&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=987acb71\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lc.ryeung/</a><br />\n訂書 （有2 本）<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/bookorder612\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fbookorder612&d=OzCpETo5oS2N7QoMCn84Cwp4YzggAwntK9UjHSQ2u7w%3D&h=47bb869a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/bookorder612</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe27cd174c761ae3254dbedcbe7dfe736c7357d","tid":2070120,"uid":219583,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:16:44.000Z","msg":"死黑鬼真係好撚煩<br />\n咁要用咩色人種 <br />\n以後落廣告不如唔好用心啦 用卡通人物算<br />\n咩色人種都比你話歧視 on99"},{"pid":"daf9a71f0aa7da04dc5c1c7cd65b481ff56d25bb","tid":2070120,"uid":125026,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-19T02:17:25.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/82902637_542246463298874_7734419528028782592_o.jpg?_nc_cat=107&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;_nc_oc=AQnROYA0T0maiKAoC6ipNuxjXFmikiJgYf2EpoaGHbv5KVdk1SW7uO3XP4zUibZzFdM&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;_nc_tp=6&amp;oh=d7dcc47c18035728c6321800dd93b4e0&amp;oe=5F10178C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F82902637_542246463298874_7734419528028782592_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D107%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26_nc_oc%3DAQnROYA0T0maiKAoC6ipNuxjXFmikiJgYf2EpoaGHbv5KVdk1SW7uO3XP4zUibZzFdM%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26_nc_tp%3D6%26oh%3D